jet::check_lock_distance.description: Assert that the value returned by tx_lock_distance is greater than or equal to the given value. Cost: 105 mWU

jet::check_lock_duration.description: Assert that the value returned by tx_lock_duration is greater than or equal to the given value. Cost: 102 mWU

jet::check_lock_height.description: Assert that the value returned by tx_lock_height is greater than or equal to the given value. Cost: 77 mWU

jet::check_lock_time.description: Assert that the value returned by tx_lock_time is greater than or equal to the given value. Cost: 93 mWU

jet::tx_is_final.description: Check if the sequence numbers of all transaction inputs are at their maximum value. Cost: 71 mWU

jet::tx_lock_distance.description: If version returns 2 or greater, then return the greatest valid Distance value of any transaction input. Return zeroes otherwise. Cost: 91 mWU

jet::tx_lock_duration.description: If version returns 2 or greater, then return the greatest valid Duration value of any transaction input. Return zeroes otherwise. Cost: 84 mWU

jet::tx_lock_height.description: If tx_is_final returns false, then try to parse the transaction's lock time as a Height value. Return zeroes otherwise. Cost: 80 mWU

jet::tx_lock_time.description: If tx_is_final returns false, then try to parse the transaction's lock time as a Time value. Return zeroes otherwise. Cost: 80 mWU
